    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1trace_1_1TracerConfig" kindref="compound">TracerConfig</ref> defines various configurable aspects of a Tracer&apos;s behavior. This class should not be used directly to configure a Tracer&apos;s behavior, instead a ScopeConfigurator should be used to compute the desired <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1trace_1_1TracerConfig" kindref="compound">TracerConfig</ref> which can then be used to configure a Tracer. </para>
